PrecisOrder authorizing the acquisition by the CANADA PORTS CORPORATION from the Department of Fisheries and Oceans of the title to a shore and deep water lot (Block 26) situated in the Township of Letellier, Quebec, at the Port of Sept-Îles, containing an area of 122,840 m², and the conveyance to the Department of National Defence of the right to use the shore portion (3,842 m²) for as long as it is needed to operate marine facilities.
